Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api

The Flow Engine base API interfaces and default record classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdvanceDataStore
    Interface for performing datastore related operations.
    AdvanceDataStoreUpdate
    Interface having only the updateXYZ methods of the datastore.
    AdvanceEngineControl
    The API for interacting with the ADVANCE Flow Engine remotely.
    AdvanceFlowCompiler
    Base interface to support compiling and verifying flows.
    AdvanceFlowExecutor
    Describes the ability to execute and terminate a list of blocks.
    AdvanceHttpListener
    Base interface for the capability to dispatch an XML message and the logged-in user name.
    AdvanceXMLCommunicator
    Base interface for classes that communicate via XML based messages.
    Copyable<T>
    Indicates if an object can create a deep copy of itself.
    HasPassword
    Interface indicating the record contains a password field which must be managed via care.
    Identifiable<K>
    Represents classes which can be asked for their unique identifier.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdvanceControlToken
    An interface representing the connection information to a remote ADVANCE Flow Engine.
    AdvanceCreateModifyInfo
    The creation/modification time and user information.
    AdvanceEmailBox
    Represents the connection information to a POP3(s)/IMAP(s) based email-box to retrieve messages.
    AdvanceEngineVersion
    Contains version information and engine details.
    AdvanceFTPDataSource
    The FTP data source record.
    AdvanceGenerateKey
    Request to generate a new key.
    AdvanceHttpAuthentication
    The record holding authentication information for basic or certificate based HTTP(s) connection.
    AdvanceJDBCDataSource
    Description of JDBC data store records.
    AdvanceJMSEndpoint
    Definition of a Java Messaging Service endpoint.
    AdvanceKeyEntry
    Properties of a concrete key in a key store.
    AdvanceKeyStore
    A record representing information about local or remote key stores.
    AdvanceKeyStoreExport
    Request for exporting a certificate from a keystore.
    AdvanceLocalFileDataSource
    A local file or directory data source.
    AdvanceRealm
    The status information about a realm.
    AdvanceSchemaRegistryEntry
    The schema registry used to ask the engine about known schemas.
    AdvanceSOAPChannel
    Describes a SOAP communication channel.
    AdvanceUser
    User settings.
    AdvanceWebDataSource
    The web data source configuration record.
    AdvanceXMLExchange
    An interface wrapping a blocking iterable which returns one or multiple values.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AdvanceEmailReceiveProtocols
    The enumeration of email box protocols.
    AdvanceEmailSendProtocols
    The enumeration for protocols of sending email.
    AdvanceFTPProtocols
    The file transfer protocols supported by ADVANCE.
    AdvanceJDBCDrivers
    Enumeration for JDBC drivers.
    AdvanceJMSDrivers
    Contains some predefined constants for JMS drivers.
    AdvanceKeyType
    The key type within the keystore.
    AdvanceLoginType
    The login types enumeration.
    AdvanceNotificationGroupType
    The notification group types.
    AdvanceRealmStatus
    The status enumeration of the ADVANCE Flow Engine Realm.
    AdvanceUserRealmRights
    The allowed realm rights for an user.
    AdvanceUserRights
    Enumeration for defining user rights.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AdvanceAccessDenied
    Exception to indicate the user has no right to perform the operation.
    AdvanceControlException
    The base exception for the ADVANCE Flow Engine Control API.
